						               													<description>Buried Beneath: A Shallow Grave is an expansion for Buried Beneath.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The gameplay is the same as the base game but the expansion adds tons of new content and also brings new modes and features to make play more difficult, varied and give you more ways to mount your defense.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;New Content:&amp;#10;7 Heroes,&amp;#10;8 Monsters,&amp;#10;4 Bosses,&amp;#10;40 Items,&amp;#10;28 Locations.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;New Actions/Stats:&amp;#10;You&amp;rsquo;ll find new symbols strewn across the village. The Looking Glass          and Hammer    offer new actions while the Gold Coins   &amp;#10;offer both a new action and act as a new stat.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;New Mechanics:&amp;#10;The shady Shop Keeper may offer helpful weapons and accessories that boost stats and give you access to one time bonuses or abilities. Make sure you buy what you want though as it might get more expensive or go out of stock!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;New Party Mode: (Adds Cooperative support)&amp;#10;&amp;ldquo;As chance would have it, an old party member of yours was visiting the day of the attack and the two of you have taken up arms once again, just like the good old days...&amp;rdquo;&amp;#10;Manage the party solo or invite a friend to help you save the village!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;quot;Rumors tell of a Travelin&amp;rsquo; Merchant more keen on linin&amp;rsquo; &amp;lsquo;is pockets wit&amp;rsquo; gold than worry about the danger of stayin&amp;rsquo; here.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Oy, it&amp;rsquo;s said he&amp;rsquo;s already setup in the village, and that &amp;lsquo;is wears is worth a lookin&amp;rsquo;&amp;hellip; What say ye, shall we pay &amp;lsquo;im a visit and see for ourselves?&amp;quot;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;-description from designer&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
